    "display_name": "AI Chat ",
    "long_instructions": "##Create a Mini Brand Kit\r\n\r\nUse AI to assist you with the following:\r\n- Create a fictional product.\r\n- Create a sample user persona\r\n- Build a mini brand kit with:\r\n\t- 3–5 color swatches\r\n\t- A font pair (heading + body text)\r\n\t- 1–2 descriptive style words (e.g., sleek, bold, approachable)\r\n- Connect your design choices for your fictional product back to the sample user persona.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
